# Cloudflare Pages SPA fallback (same proven rule the anime-only production
# site already uses on Cloudflare). On Cloudflare Pages, real files in the
# build output — including /sitemap.xml, /sitemap-*.xml and /robots.txt —
# are ALWAYS served before this rule, so they still return correct XML/text.
# We deliberately keep this file to a single rule: extra/placeholder rules can
# make Cloudflare misbehave (the cause of the previous blank screen).
# Old (dead) sitemap URL -> new sitemap index. Specific rules always win over
# the splat below on Cloudflare Pages, so this cannot affect the SPA fallback.
/sitemap.xml    /sitemap_index.xml    301

/*    /index.html    200
